Java program to swap two numbers

[Java program to swap two numbers](https://www.flowerbrackets.com/java-program-to-swap-two-numbers/)

Well, there are few ways in swapping of two numbers in java.

swap two numbers in java using temporary variable
swap two numbers in java without using temporary variable

 Now letâ€™s see java program to swap two numbers using temporary variable.

import java.util.Scanner;
public class SwapTwoNumbersInJava
{
   public static void main(String[] args)
   {
      int a;
      int b;
      int swap;
      System.out.println("Please enter two integers to swap : ");
      Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
      a = sc.nextInt();
      b = sc.nextInt();
      System.out.println("Before swap : a = " + a + "\n Before swap : b = " + b);
      swap = a;
      a = b;
      b = swap;
      System.out.println("After swap : a = " + a + "\n After swap : b = " + b);
   }
}
